 RвҶҗTEST_FRAMESVG;SVG;SVG2
вҚқ Test FRAMESVG generates fixed-height SVG frames for animation
вҚқ Two different dates must produce identical viewBox dimensions
 RвҶҗ1

вҚқ --- Frame 1: Anaheim, May 16 1974 ---
 STATEDDAYNOвҶҗJNU 5 16 1974
 STATEDTIMEвҶҗ5
 LONGвҶҗВҜ117.833
 LATвҶҗ33.767
 TIMEвҶҗLONG TIMEADJUST STATEDTIME
 DATEвҶҗSTATEDDAYNO+(TIMEГ·24)-LONGГ·360
 CALCULATEPLANETS
 CALCULATESTARS
 SVGвҶҗFRAMESVG

вҚқ Must return a character vector
 :If ~(1=вҚҙвҚҙSVG)вҲ§(''вүЎ0вҚҙSVG)
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: FRAMESVG must return a character vector'
   RвҶҗ0
   :Return
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must be non-empty
 :If 0=вүўSVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: FRAMESVG returned empty string'
   RвҶҗ0
   :Return
 :EndIf

вҚқ ViewBox must be fixed at 2320x3800
 :If ~вҲЁ/'viewBox="0 0 2320 3800"'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: viewBox not fixed at 2320x3800'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ SVG width/height attributes must match
 :If ~вҲЁ/'width="2320" height="3800"'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: SVG width/height attributes not 2320x3800'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Background rect must fill the fixed height
 :If ~вҲЁ/'height="3800" fill="#0a0a1a"'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: background rect not full fixed height'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain all map elements
 :If ~вҲЁ/'id="horizon"'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: horizon circle missing'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

 :If ~вҲЁ/'id="crosshairs"'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: crosshairs missing'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

 :If ~(вҲЁ/'>N<'вҚ·SVG)вҲ§(вҲЁ/'>S<'вҚ·SVG)вҲ§(вҲЁ/'>E<'вҚ·SVG)вҲ§(вҲЁ/'>W<'вҚ·SVG)
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: missing cardinal direction labels'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ Must contain tables (animation includes full layout)
 :If ~вҲЁ/'POSITION OF SUN, MOON AND PLANETS'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: planet table missing'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

 :If ~вҲЁ/'BRIGHT STARS'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: bright star table missing'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

 :If ~вҲЁ/'MOON PHASE'вҚ·SVG
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: moon phase missing'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

вҚқ --- Frame 2: different date, same location ---
вҚқ Dimensions must be identical regardless of sky content
 STATEDDAYNOвҶҗJNU 12 25 1974
 TIMEвҶҗLONG TIMEADJUST STATEDTIME
 DATEвҶҗSTATEDDAYNO+(TIMEГ·24)-LONGГ·360
 CALCULATEPLANETS
 CALCULATESTARS
 SVG2вҶҗFRAMESVG

 :If ~вҲЁ/'viewBox="0 0 2320 3800"'вҚ·SVG2
   вҺ•вҶҗ'FAIL: second frame viewBox not fixed at 2320x3800'
   RвҶҗ0
 :EndIf

 :If R
   вҺ•вҶҗ'PASS: TEST_FRAMESVG (',(вҚ•вүўSVG),' / ',(вҚ•вүўSVG2),' chars)'
 :EndIf
